{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"717dde0595","title":"血书：祭天地偈文","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2fb73ef657","index":0,"year":1965,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"717dde0595"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"c5892196e2","name":"林昭"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7450517574","type":"title","text":"血书：祭天地偈文","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"02c94874a1","type":"authors","text":"北京大学林昭","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"0119e7949c","type":"subtitle","text":"祭天地偈文（血书题衣）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"869f14d3d9","type":"paragraph","text":"继年月日，上海市第一看守所忍死待决之囚钦犯林昭谨以心香一瓣，米浆一盏，痛泪一掬，悲歌一曲至诚遥祭于  故市长柯公庆施之灵曰：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"662f9b2fa8","type":"paragraph","text":"鸣呼柯公，祥麟威风，鸦群独鹤，蚓虫潜龙！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"20627a12c0","type":"paragraph","text":"缜思博学，内美具足，虽在和光，见判清浊！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"b973ae4356","type":"paragraph","text":"明达治政，勤仁临民，众称劳绩，夙着贤声！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"b65213f515","type":"paragraph","text":"泰山九斗，学界师友，当朝衮衮，无出其右！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"0bbfc7fbb5","type":"paragraph","text":"公自蹈海，祸从何来！丧邦罪我，二书酿灾！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"5d9c7aff8e","type":"paragraph","text":"娥性刚烈，惟备保洁，不由旁径，似难决绝！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"05b0ddb258","type":"paragraph","text":"犹是孺黄，评审未  ，古有明训，致榻之旁！","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"b327ca2d9a","type":"paragraph","text":"徵丑初示，泄药连致，为受清名，何惧身试！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"66d4c943ae","type":"paragraph","text":"神说感依，中霄震啼，追呼    ，竟隔灵汉！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"c002098e08","type":"paragraph","text":"晨曦乍布，已扬噩讣，惊耗入耳，痛摧肝肠！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"38825a64ee","type":"paragraph","text":"当心中刀，泪决如潮，长  群踊，哀愤冲霄。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"130de30adc","type":"paragraph","text":"裂帕书誓，付彼贼子，要得解私，侠公  体。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"ca76856607","type":"paragraph","text":"朝歌声吞，暮哭招魂，天惨无色，地暗冥备。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"a2a88f2926","type":"paragraph","text":"哭公盛德，夙行谨饬，哭公治绩，曲惠生民。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"6a4a5e3305","type":"paragraph","text":"哭公雅望，民不能交，哭公卓识，举直错枉。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"79ab9ff0f1","type":"paragraph","text":"哭公长才，竟赴夜台，哭公端品，忽沉蒿莱。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"f4689f6162","type":"paragraph","text":"哭公惨殃，痛泪和血，英年不永，横遭摧折。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"b0d318b3c6","type":"paragraph","text":"未尽才仁，未展经伦，未施抱负，未济众人。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"6a110eac86","type":"paragraph","text":"苍昊汉漠，后土茫落，智士愕愕，…子碌碌。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"87ca9f882e","type":"paragraph","text":"鸣呼鸣呼，徒唤奈何！仇重山岳，恨若长河！","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"540b3ae198","type":"paragraph","text":"寸息九咽，寸喉为结，寸怀如冰，寸心似炽！","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"018dd236f6","type":"paragraph","text":"挨膺一声，月落参横，情切今也，绿绛再生。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"6d201cc976","type":"paragraph","text":"松柏巍巍，是公仪态，丽日皓晖，是公兰颜。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"e377663a5b","type":"paragraph","text":"广汉千里，是公遗体，江上青峰，是公……","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"d34a7dc3c3","type":"paragraph","text":"灵客焯炽，是公素质，湖海苍茫，是公心肠。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"a97dfa428a","type":"paragraph","text":"清风霁雨，是公隽语，掣电鸣雷，是公雄威，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"6ddf933732","type":"paragraph","text":"霜寒月白，是公散魄，长天将星，是公英灵。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"ed7b4d2ff0","type":"paragraph","text":"水上珠没，歌赋月阙；人间何世，有斯惨劫。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"6c2e0df1a9","type":"paragraph","text":"这负伯仁，誓许此身，天怜冤抑，更旨封神。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"59e47a18ed","type":"paragraph","text":"忠勤端直，幽明同职，海疆靖时，永锁护国。","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"ab89c7b78b","type":"paragraph","text":"海碧天青，昊帝多情，终成正果，莫叹零丁。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"739bd606d5","type":"paragraph","text":"灵体现合，音容职活，言笑常闻，起坐在侧。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"e2d21c53fb","type":"paragraph","text":"何以为家，负然芳  ，朱文敛艳，碧血作花。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"6fdb165776","type":"paragraph","text":"花开照夜，不祥姐嫁，九鼓未明，六月雪下。","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"206df088c6","type":"paragraph","text":"湘竹蔓林，贞娥恨深，绵绵公意，悠悠女心。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"9f9226bcea","type":"paragraph","text":"鸣呼鸣呼，青衫误我，身世自悼，马舆终古。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"bcc78d3f48","type":"paragraph","text":"侠觞千回，心宇成灰，春蚕未死，北宇声哀。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"a6f9e32f30","type":"paragraph","text":"闾阖有道，至情不老，尽命完节，大义在抱。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"f38c99ebed","type":"paragraph","text":"百汇万年，碧落黄泉，来格来享，来告哭天！","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"7753f7ca85","type":"paragraph","text":"鸣呼，哀哉！伏惟尚飨！","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"},{"id":"3a7db0d82c","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《林昭文抄》，甘粹先生2000年7月11日抄本。","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595"}],"page":{"id":"7046cc510a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"717dde0595","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}